Next, for hobs of the abovementioned present invention coated gear cutting tools 1 to 13 and the conventional coated gear cutting tools 1 to 12, under high-speed cutting conditions of;
cutting speed (rotation speed): 200m/min (1062 rpm), and
feed: 2.0 mm/rev, gear cutting was performed for gears having dimensions of; outside diameter 100 mm, length 25 mm, and number of teeth 48, and a material comprising a low-alloy steel of JIS SCr 420.
